Purpose of Application

To learn basic concepts of React instead of going in complexity

1. Learn CRUD operation
    i. Create
    ii. Read
    iii. Update
    iv. Delete
2. Without Backend API,Data stored in local storage

3. Without any UI component library

4. Without any state management library


What you will learn from this application
You will learn, how to use

1. Functional components
2. useState and useEffect Hooks
3. How to pass data from Parent to child component
4. JavaScript array
5. Applying styles in React


What we can further improve

1. Use React UI component library like Material UI,Microsoft fluentui etc
2. Use state management library like Redux
3. Use Backend application API to store data
4. Use routing
5. Use package for React form like React-Hook-Form or any package for form validation